title: Candy Jam v2.2.GAME.Android.[ACF][2014].apk
description:
Candy Jam v2.2

Blend'em! Mix'em! Jam'em!

Push the candies through the blenders - make yummy Candy Jam!

Controls:
- Swipe your finger on the screen to move UP, DOWN, LEFT or RIGHT.
- Tap X to confirm option or continue.
- Tap U to undo your move.
- Tap R to restart level.
